<title>USA: Stratosphere Corp to mull alternatives.</title>
<headline>Stratosphere Corp to mull alternatives.</headline>
<dateline>LAS VEGAS 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Stratosphere Corp said Wednesday it hired Donaldson, Lufkin &amp; Jenrette to advise it on alternatives to maximize shareholder value.</p>
<p>Possible alternatives include a debt restructuring and infusion of additional capital through a rights offering, the casino company said.</p>
<p>The company's statement did not give further details on its plans.</p>
<p>Stratosphere is 42 percent owned by Grand Casinos Inc.</p>
<p>--New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610.</p>
</text>
